<% layout("layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">
      Last updated: April 2026
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="bg-white border rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 space-y-6 text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        We collect basic account information such as username, email, role (buyer/seller), and order-related data required to operate the MediCycle platform.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">2. How We Use Data</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        Your data is used to process orders, manage listings, provide notifications, and improve platform functionality.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">3. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        We do not sell your data. Buyer and seller details are shared only as required for order fulfillment within the platform.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">4. Data Security</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        We use standard security practices to protect your data. However, no system is completely secure, and users are responsible for maintaining account confidentiality.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">5. Cookies & Sessions</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        We use session-based authentication to keep users logged in securely. No invasive tracking cookies are used.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        You can access, update, or delete your account data by contacting support or using account settings where available.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">7. Contact</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">
        For privacy-related concerns, contact us at:
        <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">support@medicycle.com</span>
      </p>
    </section>

  </div>

</div>